response.headline: 3-day Fukuoka travel itinerary featuring Daimyo vintage shops, Ippudo ramen, luxury shopping, and art museum visits
response.summary: Day 2 Fukuoka itinerary includes exploring Daimyo area vintage shops and cafes, eating ramen at the original Ippudo branch, shopping second-hand luxury at Takayama, buying omakase at Sushi Tadao, visiting Fukuoka Art Museum, and ending at yatai stalls.

location_tags: Fukuoka, 61.8K people posted about this place

extracted_text: Explore Daimyo area (vintage shops, cute cafes, eat ramen at the original branch of Ippudo)
Shop second hand luxury at Takayama
Cap off the night at yatai stalls (again)
We actually stayed here for 5 days, but I didn't include day 1 and day 5 since we mostly just ate and drank lol
